changelog:
### Iconify v6.6.0 has arrived! It has the following new changes:

## Feature Changes:
- __Icon Packs:__
    - Added volume panel icons for android 14
    - Added Nusantara wings settings icon
- __QS Icon and Label:__
    - Fixed for android 14
- __Volume Panel:__
    - Fixed track customization for android 14
- __Navigation Bar:__
    - Made gcam lag fix optional
    - Fixed pill customization for android 14
- __Misc:__
    - Removed pre-compiled overlays
    - Fixed various customizations not working on android 14
    - Fixed a situation where multiple options get enabled in same category
- __Xposed Menu:__
    - Added option to allow theming notifications for android 14
    - Allow hiding battery icon for custom battery styles
    - Separated battery hide percentage and inside percentage
    - Fixed blur intensity changer for android 14
    - Fixed QS top margin changer for android 14
    - Fixed fluid theme brightness bar track color
    - Added safer blur enabling method (might not work for some)

## App Changes:
- Improved application UI and UX
- Added Italian translation. Thanks to [@Danilo Belmonte](https://crowdin.com/profile/steve.burnside)
- Updated Turkish translation. Thanks to [@WINZORT](https://crowdin.com/profile/linuxthegoat)
- Added overlay informations in meta-data
- Added overlay category in manifest
- And many more improvements...

Also included in this version are bug fixes and other improvements.
